title: Dispenser for repositionable notes

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for dispenser for repositionable notes, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an isometric view of a dispenser for repositionable notes according to the present invention;
FIG. 2 is a top plan view of the dispenser illustrated in FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a bottom view of the dispenser illustrated in FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 4 is a left side view of the dispenser illustrated in FIG. 1, the right side view, the front view, and the rear view being a mirror image thereof.
